1.The Python interpreter has strict rules for variable names. 
Which of the following are legal Python names? If the name is not legal, state the reason.

and: Not legal: this a reserved word. 

_and: Legal

var: Legal

var1: Legal

1var: Not legal: Cannot start with a number.

my-name: Not legal: dashes are not legal characters for naming. 

your_name: Legal

COLOR: Legal

